OL,5,G```FIMPULS RAPIDPLAYG``````````````````
OL,7,GCologne played host to a charity       
OL,8,Gfestival, with the proceeds going to   
OL,9,GImpuls, a foundation dedicated to      
OL,10,Gresearch into muscular dystrophy.      
OL,12,FThe main attraction was the strongest  
OL,13,Fever rapidplay event ever held in      
OL,14,FGerman with 245 players.  The field    
OL,15,Fincluded 35 GMs, 43 IMs and one        
OL,16,Fcomputer programme!  No, not Deeper    
OL,17,FBlue, but something just as            
OL,18,Ffrightening, Fritz5, which retails     
OL,19,Fcommercially at around #89.99.         
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````5/19`
