OL,5,G```FBANKTON ALLEGROG```````````````````
OL,7,GIM Stephen Mannion, with a commanding  
OL,8,Gperformance, scoring 6/6, picked up his
OL,9,Gthird successive Bankton Allegro title.
OL,11,FIn the junior team tournament,         
OL,12,Fdefending champions, Holy Cross High   
OL,13,FSchool and Buckstone A prevailed again 
OL,14,Fto take this years Secondary and       
OL,15,FPrimaryevents.                         
OL,17,FThe sponsors of both events were: West 
OL,18,FLothian Council, SB Decorators, Jewel  
OL,19,Fand Esk Valley Collage and UNISON.     
